thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by JOHN

author: JOHN
title: JOHN
text: Excellent quality-nothing cheap about this frame. I have purchased more expensive frames of much lesser quality-never again since coming across American Frames. The packaging was so good, it took me 30 minutes to get the frame out-no possibility of damage-came out clean and in perfect condition. Considering the cost, I'm impressed beyond my expectations. I am an artist and I paint daily... This is where I will order my frames.
